          "text": "You must attach this model to one of the above units, and can do so even if one or more CHARACTER units have already been attached to that unit, but a unit can never include more than one PACK LEADER model. If you do, and that Bodyguard unit is destroyed , the Leader units attached to it become separate units, with their original Starting Strengths . If it is not possible to attach this model to a unit, it does not take part in the battle and counts as having been destroyed."
